# PRPs Directory

This directory contains Project Requirement Plans (PRPs) for feature implementation.

## Naming Convention
`{feature-name}.md` - e.g., `excel-read-helpers.md`, `chat-ui.md`

## Creating a PRP
Use the `/generate-prp` command:
```
/generate-prp excel-read-helpers
```

## Executing a PRP
Use the `/execute-prp` command:
```
/execute-prp PRPs/excel-read-helpers.md
```
